{"tid":1581893,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"收到藍絲騷擾電話應對方法","createTime":"2019-09-19T19:28:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-19T19:35:07.000Z","uid":80536,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"76ce711a0b88342791179b93b78580d396b14373","tid":1581893,"uid":80536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T19:28:19.000Z","msg":"有朋友最近被仆街藍絲起底 <br />\n不斷收到騷擾電話同msg<br />\n除左大部分133無名氏<br />\n仲有好多來自大陸同世界各地嘅電話<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XtRBonV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXtRBonV.png&h=3f5ce448&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n兼有三毛式問候<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ierasPo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FierasPo.png&h=26b83e8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n結論：<br />\n香港解密網絕對同大陸有關係<br />\n甚至有系統自動打出電話騷擾<br />\n被起底手足千萬唔好番大陸<br />\n<br />\n收到可疑電話或留言： 唔聽/無視<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n嫌太煩可以轉電話號碼<br />\n最重要調節心態 唔需要驚！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"c435294b8382e2b40c4eabc608bf49948bc0d7ab","tid":1581893,"uid":34256,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T19:35:07.000Z","msg":"你咁講法 姐係冇應對方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}